      "page": 6,
      "title": "Get An Obama Phone For Free!",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Get An Obama Phone For Free!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>5. Fraud And The Free Phone Program</h4>\n<img alt=\"Get An Obama Phone For Free!_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/get-an-obama-phone-for-free/get-an-obama-phone-for-free_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/get-an-obama-phone-for-free/get-an-obama-phone-for-free_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/get-an-obama-phone-for-free/get-an-obama-phone-for-free_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/get-an-obama-phone-for-free/get-an-obama-phone-for-free_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Cellular providers, like Total Call Mobile and TerraCom Wireless, have also been involved in deceitful practices. Lifeline has manipulated subscriber numbers for more funding. Total Call Mobile was fined $51 million for signing up fake subscribers, while TerraCom Wireless allowed unqualified individuals to have multiple phones.</p>\n</img></div>"
